      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "圣母上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00002",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "圣母"
      ],
      "text": "喜滋滋移莲步用目观望，看瑶池好华艳胜似天堂。诸神仙齐来到瑶池庆赏，因此上设寿宴齐集非常。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00003",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "圣母上高台。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00004",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "圣母"
      ],
      "text": "海屋添寿祝圣诞，福星永乐画堂前。岁岁年年逢此日，蟠桃会上会君仙。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00005",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "圣母"
      ],
      "text": "君乃，华瑶池圣母也。上帝见我广并九寿，常度众生。时命诸仙，齐赴蟠桃，为此准备筵席，候众仙降临。侍女们伺候了。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00006",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四仙女同上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00007",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "同念",
      "speakers": [
        "四仙女"
      ],
      "text": "画堂筵庆雀屏开，福禄荣华自天来。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00008",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四仙女"
      ],
      "text": "圣母在上，小仙等拜寿。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00009",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "圣母"
      ],
      "text": "众仙子平身。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00010",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四仙女"
      ],
      "text": "圣寿无疆。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00011",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "何仙姑、韩湘子、曹国舅、蓝采和、汉钟离、李铁拐、吕洞宾、张果老同上。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00012",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "吕洞宾"
      ],
      "text": "银镯煌煌瑞彩罩，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00013",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "同西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "何仙姑",
        "韩湘子",
        "曹国舅",
        "蓝采和",
        "汉钟离",
        "李铁拐",
        "张果老"
      ],
      "text": "年年此日捧蟠桃。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "90000002_e00014",
      "play_id": "90000002",
      "scene_id": "90000002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
